.:PREREQUISITS:.

Install the following python libraries
    * python 2.6
    * twisted
    * mysql-python
    * basicproperty
    * starpy

.:INSTALLATION:.

Setup an environment (virtualenv preferred), then install each of the prereqs

    % virtualenv --no-site-packages /usr/local/stargate/env
    % cd /usr/local/stargate/env
    % source bin/activate
    % pip install twisted
    % pip install mysql-python
    % mkdir /usr/local/stargate/env/src

Download basicproperty from http://basicproperty.sourceforge.net/

    % wget "http://basicproperty.sourceforge.net/.../basicproperty.tar.gz" -O \
      /usr/local/stargate/env/src/
    % cd /usr/local/stargate/env/src/
    % tar -xzf basicproperty*.tar.gz && cd basicproperty*
    % pip install .

Download starpy from http://starpy.sourceforge.net/

    % wget "http://starpy.sourceforge.net/.../starpy.tar.gz" -O \
      /usr/local/stargate/env/src/
    % cd /usr/local/stargate/env/src/
    % tar -xzf starpy*.tar.gz && cd starpy*
    % pip install .
